snippet.title: SVRVIVE: The Deus Helix - Official trailer
snippet.description:
Available on Steam now: http://store.steampowered.com/app/509540/
Released for HTC Vive on the 17th of November 2016.

Trailer music created by Sebastian Furrer from Swedish DJ Duo CAZZETTE and Simon Ring from SVRVIVE. 

Website: http://svrvive.com/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/svrvive/ 
Twitter: https://twitter.com/svrviveofficial   
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/svrviveofficial

Built with Unity and uses Simplygon (TM), Copyright (c) - 2016 Donya Labs AB.
